. The species is named after the Periyar National Park and Wildlife Sanctuary close to Thekkady, the 
<typeStatus id="9A5B884A4A60E011FF0CFD62FF67FCF6" box="[151,199,766,792]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="0DFA65634A60E011FF5CFCBEFC98FC46" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="455F36E84A60E011FF5CFCBEFC98FC46" blockId="12.[151,1437,261,936]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FF5CFCBEFE9BFCD2" bold="true" box="[199,315,802,828]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FED8FCBEFE1EFCD5" authority="Meshram, 2019" authorityName="Meshram" authorityYear="2019" box="[323,446,802,828]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="periyari" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FED8FCBEFE1EFCD5" box="[323,446,802,828]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. periyari</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FE5DFCBEFD80FCD2" bold="true" box="[454,544,802,828]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="6CA757814A60E011FE5DFCBEFD80FCD2" box="[454,544,802,828]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
resembles 
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FD04FCBEFC64FCD5" authority="Nielson" authorityName="Nielson." authorityYear="1991" box="[671,964,801,828]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kodikanelensis">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FD04FCBEFCC6FCD5" box="[671,870,801,828]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. kodikanelensis</emphasis>
Nielson
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FC67FCBEFB7AFCD2" authority="(Distant)" authorityName="Distant" baseAuthorityName="Distant" box="[1020,1242,801,828]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ostenta">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FC67FCBEFBCEFCD5" box="[1020,1134,802,828]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. ostenta</emphasis>
(Distant)
</taxonomicName>
but differs in the relative size of the aedeagal processes and ventral pygofer process. The ventral pygofer process is elongate in 
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FA18FCDAFEE3FC6D" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FA18FCDAFE9FFC6D" authorityName="Nielson." authorityYear="1991" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kodikanelensis">C. kodikanelensis</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
but it is short in 
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FE62FCF6FDC9FC6D" baseAuthorityName="Distant" box="[505,617,874,900]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ostenta">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FE62FCF6FDC9FC6D" box="[505,617,874,900]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. ostenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FD07FCF6FC3CFC6D" box="[668,924,874,900]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FD07FCF6FCBAFC6D" authorityName="Meshram" authorityYear="2019" box="[668,794,874,900]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="periyari">C. periyari</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FCB9FCF6FC3CFC6D" authorityName="Meshram" authorityYear="2019" box="[802,924,874,900]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="periyari">C. periyari</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
is much smaller (
<quantity id="82189B0D4A60E011FBC5FCF5FB15FC6A" box="[1118,1205,873,900]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.4" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="5.4">5.4 mm</quantity>
) and paler compared to 
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FF2FFC11FE86FC49" baseAuthorityName="Distant" box="[180,294,909,935]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ostenta">
C. 
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FF4EFC12FE86FC49" box="[213,294,910,935]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">ostenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<quantity id="82189B0D4A60E011FEAFFC11FE1EFC46" box="[308,446,909,936]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.8" metricValueMax="6.9" metricValueMin="6.7" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="6.8" valueMax="6.9" valueMin="6.7">6.7–6.9 mm</quantity>
) and 
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A60E011FE67FC12FD62FC49" authorityName="Nielson." authorityYear="1991" box="[508,706,909,936]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kodikanelensis">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A60E011FE67FC12FD62FC49" box="[508,706,909,936]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. kodikanelensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<quantity id="82189B0D4A60E011FD4AFC11FC8CFC46" box="[721,812,909,936]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="mm" value="7.5">7.5 mm</quantity>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
